ng <br />\nDone</blockquote><br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nskin side down<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSeason?<br />\nA touch of salt and pepper</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽完即刻識煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8dbd619897102f2a02ccd844021efd11e5c3fcb","tid":153823,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:32:22.000Z","msg":"其實牛排衣家野，同海鮮一樣，靚既唔洗搞甘多調味，鹽同黑白椒就ok，最多加D Rosemary番茜，甚至係超市買支Season $4X~6X一支就搞掂，只有肉質差既先要搞花臣，所以甘樣不如慳D錢去Citysuper或者其他出口店買勁靚牛排返屋企整仲好啦"},{"pid":"42e61af075d1cf23a6436ee51907554b7af7bd43","tid":153823,"uid":6823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"插溫度計上維基對番個表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面話6成個d真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：做過分子料理半年"},{"pid":"2e8828d64eddf4377baf4787871188cb21407218","tid":153823,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"睇高登"},{"pid":"1d79b6f4185e253b8cd48d32850a06b3e00b6dd9","tid":153823,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Hot pan<br />\nOliver oil<br />\nSkin side down<br />\nButter thyme garlic <br />\nAmazing <br />\nDone</blockquote><br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nskin side down<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSeason?<br />\nA touch of salt and pepper</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽完即刻識煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTouch of oliver oil<br />\nHot pan<br />\nLet the pan do the work<br />\n30 seconds and upside down"},{"pid":"20d86598322071c7194d6612120e62698c30cf25","tid":153823,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"我睇過一段片 係講原來不停咁反塊扒 塊扒受熱會更平均<br />\n佢仲用埋熱能黎睇<br />\n有冇人試過係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a01a2aac194595ddf665410db5aafe9def5a2d","tid":153823,"uid":16642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"個人煮法<br />\n未完全解凍就煎"},{"pid":"46ebf09b6087505c9aae731dca5278aff8737372","tid":153823,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:34:54.000Z","msg":"其實屋企煮幾成熟唔駛問人.<br />\n<br />\n你買番扒, 急凍既早一晚放番上格, 一寸以上就早好放兩晚, 如果係靚扒最好用D可以用血水分隔既盒.<br />\n<br />\n食之前早兩至四個鐘放番室溫, 自己煮扒最緊要解凍做得好, 你有做下功課塊扒一定唔太差, 解凍做得好基本不敗之地. 當你每次解凍得好, 你好快掌握煎幾耐幾成熟. 無把握就預多D時間解凍.<br />\n<br />\n煎扒有生鐵pan就最好, 重油熱到出煙再落扒每邊煎三十秒.<br />\n有信心可以keep住大火煎用手feel, 無既封晒邊再上碟俾佢抖抖.<br />\n再用中火每邊煎2分鐘至3分鐘, 咁根本上塊扒就3至7成熟.<br />\n煎左一次你就知大約點煎就可以煎到你想要既狀態."},{"pid":"a6f778a490ff17ac8557402154e9e45bd20a9174","tid":153823,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇過一段片 係講原來不停咁反塊扒 塊扒受熱會更平均<br />\n佢仲用埋熱能黎睇<br />\n有冇人試過係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過唔得, 煎完D血水係咁出.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實咩都試下先知咩啱自己, 每人有既工具口味都唔同, 無最好煮法.<br />\n<br />\n試過有FD 安格斯十成熟但全場公認極好食. 唔駛太理人點講, 食左唔得下次就番就OK.<br />\n<br />\n以前成日跟網上教學發覺多魚.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24df18c5ae2ae936b608a73d924858e3a09c5615","tid":153823,"uid":45645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我睇過一段片 係講原來不停咁反塊扒 塊扒受熱會更平均<br />\n佢仲用埋熱能黎睇<br />\n有冇人試過係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過唔得, <span style=\"color: red;\">煎完D血水係咁出</span>.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/